article_title: Red Wings vs. Sabres: Darren Helm spins, scores off backhand
article_text:
Who needs Pavel Datsyuk?

Detroit is a top-heavy team this season. Henrik Zetterberg and Pavel Datsyuk are the only Wings with more than five goals. So when Datsyuk misses a game, who does Detroit call on to score?

How about Darren Helm? He pulled off a sweet, Datsyukian move on Sunday to tie the game at 1-1.
